   <p xml:id="140" begin="00:03:14.756" end="00:03:20.295">CRIMES THAT HE COMMITTED.</p>
   <p xml:id="141" begin="00:03:16.157" end="00:03:21.396">&gt;&gt; WELL,L, I DONT KNOW ABOUT</p>
