   <p xml:id="143" begin="00:03:21.462" end="00:03:23.197">JURISDICTIONS SOFT ON CRIME.</p>
   <p xml:id="144" begin="00:03:22.897" end="00:03:26.501">DO I KNOW.</p>
   <p xml:id="145" begin="00:03:23.264" end="00:03:28.403">THIS THERE ISNT ONE</p>
