   <p xml:id="147" begin="00:03:28.469" end="00:03:30.538">GOOD POINT TO BE MADE.</p>
   <p xml:id="148" begin="00:03:29.671" end="00:03:31.406">I HAD AN ARGUMENT WITH</p>
