   <p xml:id="158" begin="00:03:43.284" end="00:03:45.587">FROM.</p>
   <p xml:id="159" begin="00:03:44.385" end="00:03:46.220">YOU DONT LET THEM O OUT AND</p>
   <p xml:id="160" begin="00:03:45.653" end="00:03:47.055">GIVE THEM BAIL.</p>
   <p xml:id="161" begin="00:03:46.287" end="00:03:47.422">THATS EXACTLY WHAT</p>
